    git sparse-checkout set apps/frontend .agents .cursor .github .husky products/static tools/dotenvx-cli packages/i18n packages/fe-environment packages/platform products/form-templates products/agreement-gen packages/datadog-logger packages/lumin-kit packages/redis-client packages/shell-ui scripts packages/lumin-design-system products/pdf products/sign

